reviewText: Great horror movie, lots of action, twisted thriller, and must watch. Great for your horror collection. Definitely would want to view it every year along with your Halloween choice of scarry movies.
Great movie scary yet a great mystery in the plot as to who the killer really is. A must see. :)
Excellent Horror Flick! Check out Little O's character he is a good actor! Poor legless kid! This thriller is action packed!
